data.description: Move right into this wonderful, updated brick ranch in prime location close to shopping, minutes from highways, right next to CCBC. This house sits on a large, level corner lot and has a wrap-around concrete patio and a wood deck perfect for entertaining. The one-car integral garage and the two-car detached garage offer plenty of covered parking space. The huge family room in the lower level is ready for a man-cave or a play room. On the main floor you will find an almost new kitchen with stainless appliances, a dining room and a spacious, bright living room with gas fireplace. These common areas and the main bedroom have beautiful hardwood floors. The three bedrooms share the gorgeous tiled bathroom with heated floors, which is accessible from the main bedroom directly, as well as from the hall. You can enjoy radiant heat in the cold months, and the central AC system keeps you cool in summer.
